* HMS &quot;Buttercup&quot;, a list of vessels built for the Royal Navy
* Little Buttercup or Santa Fe No. 5, an 0-4-0 steam locomotive 
* Sicilian Buttercup chicken, a breed of chicken
* Peanut butter cup, a chocolate candy</text><links>
